Performance
-----------

* kernel param: mitigations=off
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Improving_performance#Turn_off_CPU_exploit_mitigations


* tune2fs -O fast_commit /dev/<nvme0n1p2>
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Ext4#Enabling_fast_commit

* laptop
w /sys/devices/system/cpu/cpufreq/policy*/energy_performance_preference - - - - performance

Quirks
------
* possible laptop touchpad fix
echo 'ACTION=="add|change", SUBSYSTEM=="i2c", KERNELS=="i2c-CUST0001:00", ATTR{power/control}="on"' | sudo tee /etc/udev/rules.d/99-touchpad-power.rules

reload it if needed now:
sudo udevadm control --reload-rules
sudo udevadm trigger

Then check if the setting applied:
cat /sys/devices/pci0000:00/0000:00:15.1/i2c_designware.1/i2c-10/i2c-CUST0001:00/power/control
